casebody.data:
Jason Michael ZANK, petitioner,
v.
Liz Lorena LOPEZ MORENO. No. 18-661. Supreme Court of the United States March 18, 2019.

Motion of Reunite International Child Abduction Centre for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.
